Date: Fri, 17 Apr 2026 13:16:50 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Fix facade nav: hamburger opens menu, wordmark links
 home, My Logs section for real data

- FacadeHeader on /pitch/sleep now uses a real button + SavyMobileMenu for the hamburger (was decorative). The SAVY. wordmark is a Link to /.
- SavyMobileMenu gets a "My Logs" section under the main nav with direct-route links to /sleep, /mood, /nutrition (bypassing pitchHref) so Adam can always reach his real data in one tap from any page.

Made-with: Cursor
